{"tid":1040744,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"其實假膠文化係咪已經唔存在？","createTime":"2019-02-28T10:10:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-01T11:34:16.000Z","uid":135638,"like":17,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"242ded6f46c1c7b6ada8f41588241b1f572b69f7","tid":1040744,"uid":135638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T10:10:58.000Z","msg":"見有啲人扮假膠都扮得幾明顯<br />\n好似下面個post咁<br />\n<br />\n好多香港人都唔識dude呢個字<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1040563\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1040563</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n條友擺明特登打錯pleasure做pressure<br />\n智商高過60嘅應該都知樓主唔係真心<br />\n但係下面就一堆留言笑佢打錯 話佢唔識英文<br />\n配合佢扮假膠嘅人越嚟越少<br />\n以前高登好似唔係咁<br />\n無咁多懶係醒嘅留言<br />\n假膠文化係咪已經唔存在？"},{"pid":"28bee2238f1ec21c1b35fbf5b44f75a8f418c3d9","tid":1040744,"uid":2419,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T10:12:51.000Z","msg":"吹呀 屌你老母"},{"pid":"08e671c15432f70c28663776c5853588dc894495","tid":1040744,"uid":201823,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T10:12:59.000Z","msg":"太多認真撚+ 有啲假膠真係唔好笑"},{"pid":"fea8de07640aed66fb5dc7695545133a3f85fcbf","tid":1040744,"uid":176802,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T10:15:31.000Z","msg":"無啲質素又唔好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9be4dc5c3dbce57ead5f0aae91ad3b617924de9","tid":1040744,"uid":27510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T10:17:08.000Z","msg":"因為依家得返真心膠"},{"pid":"7570f2b38aefb58aaf624b7f283f98e42973f699","tid":1040744,"uid":107927,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T10:17:11.000Z","msg":"假膠常用的招數<br />\n<br />\n扮真心膠，如當有人用「goodest」去取笑別人英文差時，他就會扮不知「goodest」的典故說：「咩叫『goodest』？係『best』呀，英文咁差仲笑人」，博取旁人以為自己是真心膠。"},{"pid":"37b36d0e1bfc0cd1df9978116ccb02d0280ca1f1","tid":1040744,"uid":92859,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T10:18:01.000Z","msg":"Block哂<br />\n懶得睇假膠post"},{"pid":"ba1c9bcb2